<title>USA: Insignia promotes Aston to CFO.</title>
<headline>Insignia promotes Aston to CFO.</headline>
<dateline>GREENVILLE, S.C. 1996-08-21</dateline>
<text>
<p>Insignia Financial Group Inc said Wednesday it named James Aston chief financial officer and promoted Ronald Uretta to the new post of chief operating officer.  </p>
<p>Aston previously served as a member of Insignia's Office of the Chairman, the real estate services company said.</p>
<p>In addition to Uretta's new repsonsibilities, he will continue to serve as treasurer, the company said.</p>
<p>Uretta will oversee corporate accounting, human resources, corporate facilities management, and information technology.</p>
<p>-- New York Newsdesk 212-859-1610</p>
